{"tid":1377142,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[World of Warcraft] 回鍋仔招攬大秘境隊員","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:06:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T13:06:01.000Z","uid":290626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2e646cb016d717f64b5882dee1ee12dade40e2","tid":1377142,"uid":290626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"8.2 回鍋後想組隊固定隊沖層大秘境, 想組團既原因係聽唔慣普通話指揮，想Form一 Team識講識聽廣東話既隊友<br />\n自己而家得一隻人, 實裝427聖騎, 主奶副DD, 暗語眾server<br />\n另外速升緊一隻小D, 之後可能會升埋隻 獵人/薩滿<br />\n想搵T, 2隻近程DD, 1隻遠程DD,或者補都可以<br />\n主要活動時間待定，等Form到Team 再傾<br />\n<a href=\"http://有意者可以PM我你既battle.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5PM%E6%88%91%E4%BD%A0%E6%97%A2battle.net&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=1dc64728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">有意者可以PM我你既battle.net</a> id, 如果純想識多個朋友,<a href=\"http://都可以PM我你既battle.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%83%BD%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5PM%E6%88%91%E4%BD%A0%E6%97%A2battle.net&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=a024645f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">都可以PM我你既battle.net</a> id (畢竟係香港仲有玩魔獸既人真係好少)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aE5fcOH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaE5fcOH.png&h=6c3b47b3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外想搵一個穩定打到H永恆既公會入,已經唔想再過係野團食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目前個人只得H1-6經驗, 有開荒M難度 (7.0有打M夢魘、M暗夜堡同M王座)<br />\n精練期間可以打到2萬4+ DPS 同 3萬+ HPS (為野團數據)<br />\n<a href=\"http://有意者同樣可以PM我你既battle.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9C%89%E6%84%8F%E8%80%85%E5%90%8C%E6%A8%A3%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5PM%E6%88%91%E4%BD%A0%E6%97%A2battle.net&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDaVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=e29ad63e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">有意者同樣可以PM我你既battle.net</a> id<br />\n<br />\n利申: 聯盟汪, 部落大佬們輕力D<br />\n最後一句:<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div>"}]}